4Geeks Academy offers a Data Science & Machine Learning course that prepares students to become professional Data Analysts. The course covers Python, SQL, Looker (Google Data Studio), Streamlit, and Statistics. Students will learn to create predictive models, work with algorithms like Close Neighbors and Decision Trees, and master industry-standard tools. The course duration is 16 weeks, with 3 classes weekly and a maximum of 12 students per class. No previous experience is required, and certificates recognized by multiple organizations are awarded upon completion. Classes are available in English or Spanish. For more information, visit the website: https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning. stop